    <abstract id="aspace_dfd4c037e0969cae0cdf34c9f8364b1b">This artifical collection contains materials about eighteenth and nineteenth state and private lotteries held in the eastern and midwestern United States.</abstract>
    <physloc id="aspace_1079146f43c9f4added2a1be09e525e1">The materials are located onsite in the department.</physloc>
