  <scopecontent id="aspace_7f2a2f0e640d15d446e685c3d13e4765">
    <head>Content Description</head>
<p>This artifical collection consists of advertisements and broadsides for lotteries, newspaper clippings about lotteries, and lottery tickets.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <processinfo id="aspace_ec237279f096e96d56e87170a7c3b1ed">
    <head>Processing Information</head>
<p>Processed by Jodi Boyle in 2021.</p>  </processinfo>
  <arrangement id="aspace_ea65e6287fadb22430a2472ef7d117ff">
    <head>Arrangement of the Collection</head>
<p>The collection is organized alphabetically.  There are no series.</p>  </arrangement>
  <acqinfo id="aspace_36caffeaeb020f01e04c73348d4ab15a">
    <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
<p>The exact provenance of this collection is unknown, but these items were all purchased individually by the University Libraries.</p>  </acqinfo>
