  <bioghist id="aspace_f24090f841be8b65c08dafaf4e946fa5">
    <head>Historical Note</head>
<p>This collection documents how the United States in its early decades had both public and private lotteries and how advertisements and broadsides strongly tried to encourage individuals to buy tickets and participate/gamble in these upcoming lotteries.</p>  </bioghist>
